latestIgtvVideos.title: Dyson Airwrap - Ariana Grandes wedding look.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I lovee my Airwrap by Dyson. @dyson_india 
It’s a machine that does it all. From drying to smoothening to curls and all that. But what is the coolest thing is the technology they use. The styler harnesses an aerodynamic phenomenon called the coanda effect. It curves air to attract and wrap hair to the barrel. You have to see some videos to believe it. 
.
Here I have used almost of the attachments to get Arianas wedding look. Sleek half tied hair and soft curls at the bottom using the 30mm barrel. And loveddd they way it turned out. 
.
- An expensive product but you get your moneys worth if you use it after every wash. You get salon like hair at home. 
- for those who think the curls will open up please use a mousse before styling and a hair spray after styling. I promise then your curls won’t open. 
- you can choose between hot air and cold air. 
- one tip is to keep your hair slight damp when you are curling your hair. Like don’t dry it completely before. This way you are able to control your hair and will get the most gorgeous curls ever. 
.
#dysonairwrap #dysonhair #dysonindia #airwrapreview #dysonreview #arianagrande #arianagrandelook #arianagrandewedding #arianagrandeweddingphotos #hairtutorial #halftiedhair #hairstyles #arianagrandehairstyle #arianagrandemakeup #trendingigtv #trending #igtvhairstyles #theallyedit

latestIgtvVideos.title: @themohalife 5 in 1 hair oil.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I keep getting compliments for my long healthy hair and often asked about the secret to maintain it. While choosing the right shampoo is important, I believe in oiling my hair twice a week in Typical Ayurvedic Indian Style or Siro Abhyanga. 
Choose a hair oil that is 100% Ayurvedic and free from mineral oils & paraffin. I choose MOHA: 5 in 1 hair oil, it is a mix of 5-oils and takes complete care of scalp & hair like Dandruff, Hairfall, Slipt-ends etc. and Promotes Growth. 
After applying oil on your hair massage it regularly.Keep it for at least 2-hours, for best results. It will help boost the strength and texture of your hair. It also improves your sleep,calms your mind,gives relief from headaches and stress and prevents premature  greying of your hair.
Apart from regular oiling, I used moha: 5 in 1 hair oil for fortnightly hair masks too like: with Aloe or Egg, herbal shampoo & serum for clean, healthy & soft hair that smells amazing all day long.
.
#charakpharma #moha #mohanaturals #moha5in1hairoil #mohahairoil #theallyedit #mohaayurveda
